headline: These 2 High-Yield Dividend Stocks Are Making History – and They Have Generous Payouts
summary: Kinder Morgan and Phillips 66 have teamed up on the Western Gateway Pipeline, a first-of-its-kind route sending refined fuels from Texas to California, Arizona, and Nevada—expected to move up to 200,000 barrels per day and ease West Coast supply shortages.
